China claimed its first gold at the Beijing 2022 Olympic Winter Games from the 2,000m mixed relay of short-track speed skating on Saturday.China, consisting of Fan Kexin, Qu Chunyu, Ren Ziwei and Wu Dajing, won the gold in 2 minutes and 37.348 seconds.Â Italy and Hungary took the silver and bronze medals respectively. (With input from Xinhua)